[SN]TITLE[SN]
Devon rapist Adrian Jewell did 'untold damage'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man who raped and sexually assaulted two teenagers has been jailed for 19 years.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Handyman Adrian Jewell was also convicted of voyeurism after secretly filming another girl in a bathroom.
Exeter Crown Court heard one victim was 12 when he first raped her, in Devon. The abuse continued until she was 13.
The crimes were first reported to police in 2006 but Jewell went on to commit further offences before being arrested in 2015.
